                "invention-title": [
                    "Solar-driven circuit board pyrolysis hydrogen production and metal recovery co-production process",
                    "一种太阳能驱动的电路板热解制氢和回收金属联产工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a co-production process for hydrogen production and metal recovery by rapidly pyrolyzing a circuit board with molten salt driven by solar energy. Fused salt has good heat and mass transfer characteristics, the tower type solar condensation reflecting plate is used for heating the fused salt, energy consumption and carbon emission needed in the pyrolysis process are reduced, the cost is saved, rapid pyrolysis of the waste circuit board is achieved, resources are recycled, chemical raw materials such as hydrogen are prepared, the waste circuit board is fully pyrolyzed, and the waste circuit board pyrolysis efficiency is improved. And the harm to the environment is effectively reduced. According to the scheme, operation is easy, energy consumption is low, the dual pressure of fossil resource shortage and environmental pollution at present can be relieved, and the method has wide application prospects in the field of comprehensive utilization of organic hazardous waste."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种太阳能驱动熔融盐快速热解电路板制氢和回收金属的联产工艺。本发明利用熔融盐具有较好的传热传质特性，用塔式太阳能聚光反射板来实现对熔融盐的加热，降低了热解过程所需能耗与碳排放，节约了成本，实现废弃电路板的快速热解，既回收了资源、制备了氢气等化工原料，更将废弃电路板充分热解，有效的减少了对环境的危害。本发明的方案操作简单且能耗低，可缓解当前化石资源匮乏与环境污染的双重压力，在有机危废的综合利用领域有着广阔的应用前景。"
                }
            ]
